title: Voxel - Camping
description: Voxel Camping is a library of high detail voxel exterior props assets to use in your projects.
longDescription:
Subscribe to my Newsletter to never miss out on releases and discounts!


Voxel Camping is a library of high detail voxel exterior props to use in your game.


Assets included :

  • Axe
  • Backpack (5 Color Variants)
  • Barbecue
  • Binoculars
  • Camera
  • Canoe (5 Color Variants)
  • Canoe Container
  • Canopy (5 Color Variants)
  • Chair (5 Color Variants)
  • Cooking Pot
  • Cooking Stands (Wood and Metal)
  • Cup
  • Field Bed (5 Color Variants)
  • Firecamp (Voxel Fire VFX included)
  • Fishing Rod (5 Color Variants)
  • Flashlight (5 Color Variants)
  • Frying Pan
  • Gas Cooker
  • Gas Can
  • Gas Tanks (Small and Medium)
  • Ghetto Blaster
  • Guitar
  • Ice Box (5 Color Variants)
  • Jerrycan (5 Color Variants)
  • Kayak (5 Color Variants)
  • Lantern (5 Color Variants)
  • Various logs from small to large
  • Log Pile
  • Medkit
  • Paddles (Simple and Double, 5 Color Variants)
  • Picnic Table
  • Power Bank
  • Relaxer (5 Color Variants)
  • Sauce Pan
  • Shovel
  • Sleeping Bags (Rolled and Unrolled, (5 Color Variants))
  • Solar Panels
  • Camping Stool (5 Color Variants)
  • Camping Tables (2 Types, 5 Color Variants)
  • Tents (3 Types, 5 Color Variants)
  • Thermos (5 Color Variants)
  • Walkie Talkie (5 Color Variants)
  • Water Bottle


High-detail voxel models are not recommended for mobile.
technicalDetails:
Number of Unique Meshes: 55

Collision: Yes - Automatically Generated

Vertex Count: 136 - 8722

LODs: No

Number of Materials and Material Instances: 2

Number of Textures: 1

Texture Resolutions: 1x256

Supported Development Platforms:

Windows: Yes

Mac: Not tested, but should work as it is an art asset

Important/Additional Notes: High-detail voxel models are not recommended for mobile games
